                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName>, chargé, to
                            Mr. <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 50.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-09-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 19,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Naval engagement off North Korea 17th; five Chinese, three Japanese vessels
                        reported destroyed; fleet at Port Arthur.</p>
